src:
Arlanda har dyraste parkeringen i EU
Arlanda har den högsta parkeringsavgiften av alla flygplatser i EU, enligt en jämförelse. Dyrare än stora flygplatser som Heathrow i London och Paris Charles de Gaulle.
02 Nov 2019, 13:42 by Jenny Petersson

text:
Arlanda has the most expensive parking in the EU
Arlanda has the highest parking fee of all airports in the EU, according to a comparison. More expensive than major airports like Heathrow in London and Paris Charles de Gaulle.
02 Nov 2019, 13:42 by Jenny Petersson
